Time-Piece-HTTP version 0.003

This module adds a few HTTP-specific methods to Time::Piece package.
You might use this instead of Time::Piece itself.
The methods in this module corresponds to HTTP::Date's one. 

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


DEPENDENCIES

Time::Piece 1.20 or later
Time::Local

